Package: courseR
Type: Package
Title: R Markdown tool for generation course websites and managing assignments
Description: This package implements my workflow for (1) creating websites for
    teaching courses in R and (2) using an R package to semi-automation student
    homework assignment tasks in a managed environment (e.x. RStudio server)
Version: 0.4
Date: 2017-01-06
Author: Gregg Whitworth
